# API Specification

<div class="tracey-req" id="r-api.error-format"><a class="tracey-req-anchor" href="#r-api.error-format">api.error-format</a></div>

> API errors must follow this format:
>
> ```json
> {"error": "message", "code": 400}
> ```

Regular paragraph after the blockquote.

<div class="tracey-req" id="r-api.retry-policy+2"><a class="tracey-req-anchor" href="#r-api.retry-policy+2">api.retry-policy+2</a></div>

> Clients SHOULD retry with exponential backoff.
